^foo-\\w+\$           foo@maildir.localdomain

# Perhaps a bad idea, since it encourages use of the today-pattern without persisting.
# Only useful for one-shot uses.
# Also, it's rather hard to read :-/
"^(?:\\\\w+-)+${run{/usr/bin/date +%Y%m%d}{${substr{-1}{$value}}}}\\$"        today@maildir.localdomain
